#HAVE EMPTY dataset AND trainer FOLDERS BEFORE RUNNING New_User_Dataset_and_trainer.py, HAVE haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml IN SAME FOLDER AS PROGRAM#
https://github.com/Itseez/opencv/tree/master/data/haarcascades

1.Use New_User_Dataset_and_trainer.py to create a dataset of the face you want recognised and enter an id number 1 larger than the last(starting at 1), thise will edit the trainer yml file
2.in facerecognition.py add the name of the person in the names array in the order of ID number
3.Run facerecognition.py and the program will try to find the best match for the face it's presented and prints the name into user.txt
